title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Santo in the Treasure of Dracula
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Santo in the Treasure of Dracula
description:
In this episode of Weirdhouse Cinema, Rob and Joe dive into one of Mexican luchador El Santo's various horror cinema adventures -- and not just any Santo film but the legendary "Santo In The Treasure of Dracula," which features time travel, Dracula and more.
